data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Back on the market due to no fault of the property, financing fell through not related to the property.  2016 Built Galen Model, One owner, move in ready home with brand NEW ROOF in 2023, located in the active and gated community of Del Tierra. With low HOA fee and no CDD fee, enjoy the Resort style Community Pool, fitness center, playground, soccer practice field, miles of sidewalks, common area maintenance, and manager included in the HOA services provided. With thoughtful design and flexible floorplan this two story home offers 4-Bedrooms, 2 and a half Bathrooms, PLUS a Room for a den-office (BONUS ROOM to flex as possible 5th BEDROOM) and a 2-Car garage. Enter through the foyer to a light-filled kitchen, dining, and gathering room that opens with sliders out to the spacious and fenced rear yard ready for your potted plants and herbs, playground equipment or dog-run. The Main floor has beautiful custom end-grain wood look tile for easy care, finished storage under the stairs and storage shelving in the large 2 car garage.  Enjoy the Chef’s kitchen center island with bar seating and spacious walk-in pantry perfect for entertaining. The Primary suite is huge and features a spacious walk-in closet and roomy en-suite bath with dual sink vanity, shower, water closet and linen closet. The Den/office/5th bedroom on first floor with half bath allows for a variety of uses.  Upstairs lives as a split floorplan with Primary suite separated by common area and stairwell. To accommodate a busy household and/or multiple guests the second bathroom has a tub/shower combo, dual sink vanity plus a linen closet nearby. The home is located on a road with a cul-de-sac for less traffic flow. Del Tierra is a 610 home community established in 2014.  The Del Tierra community is well known for being active in Christmas and Halloween lights and decorations as well as food truck Friday events. So Convenient to the Fort Hamer Bridge and BOAT RAMP, Lakewood Ranch, downtown Bradenton, Hospital and Business district, I-75, Anna Maria Island, Bradenton Beach, Holmes Beach, Benderson Park, UTC, Siesta Key, Lido Beach and downtown Sarasota. Easy Commute to St. Pete and Tampa International airport. Move-in ready, quick closing possible, Book your showing today!
